headline: 3 Reasons FAST is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Fastenal’s 26.7% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 21.4%, and its stock price has climbed to $46.77 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
